               <p>Richard Wall. I took in pawn a worsted gown from a woman. I cannot say the prisoner is the woman. She pawned it in the name of 
               <persName id="t17750913-45-person418">
                  Mary
                   Blackman
               <interp inst="t17750913-45-person418" type="surname" value="Blackman"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17750913-45-person418" type="given" value="Mary"></interp>
